Hello everyone,

Greeting from I&AR Student Council!

We are excited to celebrate DaanUtsav festival and welcome you to
experience the joy of giving. You have a chance to volunteer by becoming a
part of MRTS Railway stations artwork painting and also by conducting
fun-awareness activities in Fuel stations.




Daan Utsav
